---

The `novnc-patched/` directory contains a vendored and locally patched copy of
noVNC (https://github.com/novnc/noVNC), Copyright (C) The noVNC Authors,
distributed under the Mozilla Public License 2.0 (MPL-2.0). That code remains
under its original license; see the file headers in `novnc-patched/` and the
upstream project for the full license text. Local patches add macOS
Command/Super-to-Control key mapping for the broker's web viewer.
